sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant C as Client
    participant Wk as Worker
    participant H as Handler
    participant M as Manager
    participant R as Redis
    C->>H: POST /events/abc + body
    H->>M: OnStreamAppend · arm_wake (no lease yet)
    M->>R: append {type:wake} to wake_stream · manager.go
    Wk->>H: GET /wake/pool — poll the wake stream
    H-->>Wk: wake event · subscription_id, generation
    Wk->>H: POST /__ds/subscriptions/sub-1/claim {worker}
    H->>R: EVALSHA claim.lua — CAS · ZADD lease · routes.go
    R-->>H: CLAIMED · generation, wake_id, token, streams
    H-->>Wk: 200 · claim snapshot + lease_ttl_ms
    Wk->>H: POST .../ack {wake_id, generation, acks, done:true}
    H->>R: EVALSHA ack.lua — fence · ack · release
    H-->>Wk: 200 {ok:true, next_wake:false}
